items.translator_note: This medal's name is a pun on the Alien Swarm achievement 'Hat Trick', which awarded a TF2 hat for completing two missions in multiplayer.
items.description_brazilian: Isto não é um chapéu ou uma medalha. É um adesivo comemorativo.
items.description_english: The trick is, this isn't a hat or a medal. It's a commemorative sticker.
items.description_german: Der Trick ist, dass es sich nicht um einen Hut oder eine Medaille handelt. Es ist ein Gedenkaufkleber.
items.description_italian: Il trucco sta nel fatto che non è ne un cappello ne una medaglia. È uno sticker commemorativo.
items.description_japanese: 勲章でも帽子でもない偽物。実はただのステッカーである。
items.description_russian: Фокус в том, что это не шляпа и не медаль. Это памятная наклейка.
items.description_schinese: 关键是，这不是一顶帽子或一枚勋章。这是一张纪念贴纸。
items.after_description_brazilian: Alcance a conquista "Pronto para Servir" no Team Fortress 2 para destravar.
items.after_description_english: Complete the Ready For Duty achievement in Team Fortress 2 to unlock.
items.after_description_german: Schließe die Errungenschaft "Einsatzbereit" in Team Fortress 2 ab, um sie freizuschalten.
items.after_description_italian: Completa l'achievement "Pronto al Dovere" in Team Fortress 2 per sbloccarlo.
items.after_description_japanese: Team Fortress 2で「任務の準備完了」の実績を完了することでアンロックされる。
items.after_description_russian: Получите достижение «К бою готов» в Team Fortress 2, чтобы разблокировать её.
items.after_description_schinese: 在 Team Fortress 2 中完成 Ready For Duty 成就即可解锁。

items.translator_note: This medal's name is a pun about needing to go to the toilet very badly.
items.name_japanese: 大なり小なり優先順位がある
items.description_english: While infested and on fire, found the time to flush a toilet.
items.description_german: Brennend und befallen die Toilette benutzt.
items.description_italian: Mentre sei infestato e vai a fuoco, trova il tempo per tirare lo sciacquone.
items.description_japanese: 寄生された上に炎上している最中に、トイレを流す暇を見つけた。
items.description_russian: Во время инвазии и горения нашёл время, чтобы спустить воду в туалете.
